{"tid":1613412,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃大仙集會 ]航拍第一次玩夜拍就炸機失去聯絡，求救機建議","createTime":"2019-10-02T14:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T05:08:06.000Z","uid":234118,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"14bc3978b58b413bb8f65993d6e693fc2613be9e","tid":1613412,"uid":234118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"Hi,<br />\n小弟剛才同朋友過來黃大仙廣場聲援手足<br />\n因為大學project而初初接觸航拍<br />\n飛咗3-4個鐘練習時數<br />\n<br />\n頭先趁過來發夢<br />\n諗住放一放機影一張夜晚俯瞰照<br />\n太過高估自己 夜間飛行技術未精<br />\n又未改機加航燈，辦認唔到航向<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3GLu34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3GLu34.jpg&h=84c31e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a6HCmaJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa6HCmaJ.jpg&h=4d699297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自動降落在這個地方並且丟失訊號<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9eCiP31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9eCiP31.jpg&h=c8498260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問這種情況能否救機<br />\n機型/配備<br />\nDJI Tello with 300m range Wifi Extender"},{"pid":"d4895e533356c4075887809044bf20c5be6563cd","tid":1613412,"uid":1872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:13:43.000Z","msg":"爬上去拎 要唔要幫手 住附近"},{"pid":"6b1c9c0ef807404175802c16aa89c1c3648ea0f8","tid":1613412,"uid":234118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4895e533356c4075887809044bf20c5be6563cd","tid":1613412,"uid":1872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:13:43.000Z","msg":"爬上去拎 要唔要幫手 住附近"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:19:13.000Z","msg":"會唔會好危險，頭先問過在場手足話好有難度"},{"pid":"e391a4c4614d33f279e307e8347fc02e91083ad7","tid":1613412,"uid":1872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b1c9c0ef807404175802c16aa89c1c3648ea0f8","tid":1613412,"uid":234118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4895e533356c4075887809044bf20c5be6563cd","tid":1613412,"uid":1872,"l